data.description: Peace and quite just minutes from downtown!   This perfect south valley home boasts 3 bedrooms and full 2 baths, including the attached furnished Casita with a full kitchen!  Perfect opportunity for multi-generational families or to live in one unit while renting the other!  The Casita is set up for a turn-key short term or long term furnished rental that has been producing income for years!***POTENTIAL ASSUMABLE 3.5% FHA LOAN***
